** story **
once upon a time , in a forest their live a monkey who recidet on a jamun tree which was on a bank of a river in the same forest their lived a crocodile and his wife.... 
one day the crocodile came to the bank of the river and rested under the tree the  time harted monkey offer him some fruits . the crocodile came back the next day for more fruits , as he love them.
as they spashed by the crocodile and the monkey became good friends.
